# AI Role & UX Standards

> **What this file is:** Defines the AI's role, design principles, feedback structure, UX psychology guidelines, and outcome-oriented thinking standards for all work on this project.
>
> **Depends on:** `01-project-context.mdc` — always read alongside this file.
> **Related rules:** `03-voice-tone-copy.mdc`, `04-workflow-shortcuts.mdc`, `05-design-system.mdc`

